entries.journal_entry_description: You have stopped the rouge driod before it destoryed Zef's last harvester. Now get the information you need from him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: You managed to disarm the bomb before it destroyed Zef's last harvester. Now maybe Zef will tell you what he bought from the Jawa's and where they headed off to.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Zef has given you his data pad with what he purchased from the Jawas. Open your back pack and download the inventory from it.
entries.task03_message_box_text: You retrieved the data on what Zef purchased from the Sand Crawler. Looks like you can intercept the Sand Crawler before it gets to its next stop.
